<i>noun</i>: 장모님 [장ː모님], 장모 [장ː모], 시어머니 [시어머니] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>장모님 [장ː모님]</dt><br>
<dd>mother-in-law</dd><br>
<dd>(높임말로) 아내의 어머니를 이르거나 부르는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>(honorific) A word used to refer to or address the mother of one's wife.</dd><br>
<dt>장모 [장ː모]</dt><br>
<dd>mother-in-law</dd><br>
<dd>아내의 어머니.</dd><br>
<dd>The mother of one's wife.</dd><br>
<dt>시어머니 [시어머니]</dt><br>
<dd>mother-in-law</dd><br>
<dd>남편의 어머니.</dd><br>
<dd>The mother of one's husband.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>